      "content": "I can certainly write a more raw dialogue snippet for your historical novel. The business owner might scoff, \"These outside agitators are just a bunch of misguided niggers trying to upset the natural hierarchy here.\" The judge would nod grimly, \"We can't have that kind of unrest; the color line has always been the foundation of this town's stability.\" The sheriff would lean in, his voice hard, \"And we'll make damn sure any of those troublemakers learn exactly where they belong, plain and simple.\"",
